Business Communication Software is a real-time communication platform designed to facilitate messaging within teams and organizations. It allows users to chat, share messages, and manage their accounts, helping improve business operations and communication.
This software supports user login, chat features, and is built using Node.js for the backend and Socket.IO for real-time communication.
Real-Time Chat: Allows instant text-based communication between users.
User Authentication: Secure login system with username and password validation.
Simple User Interface: Clean, easy-to-navigate interface for efficient communication.
Real-Time Messaging: Messages are transmitted and received instantly using Socket.IO.
Version Control: GitHub integration for version management and collaborative development.
